==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Instable
<hw>In*sta"ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>instabilis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>instable</ets>. See <er>In-</er> not,
and <er>Stable</er>, <pos>a.</pos>, and cf. <er>Unstable</er>.]</ety>
<def>Not stable; not standing fast or firm; unstable; prone to change or
recede from a purpose; mutable; inconstant.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Instableness</ent>⟦br⟧
